model.name: Starboard Wedge Sandal
model.disambiguatingDescription: The Starboard wedge sandal captures the relaxed spirit of summer with its chunky sole in natural braided rope, inspired by the classic and chic espadrille. Its upper is crafted from calf leather and the refined Since 1854 Jacquard, a striking pattern of Monogram Flowers and an 1854 inscription in tribute to the year the House was founded. This model is finished with a rubber outsole.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Ecru/Natural
  • Since 1854 Jacquard textile and plain calf leather
  • Rope sole
  • Rubber outsole
  • 4 cm / 1.6-inch wedge heel
  • Monogram studs
  • Louis Vuitton-engraved buckle
  • Made in Italy
